author: @danieletaddei3577
text: Thanks to Jihyo and Tzuyu for their ability to relax me. Hard day at work but with these specials everything becomes easier. I really enjoyed this special. Jihyo and Tzuyu together in a very relaxed atmosphere. Two different personalities that together manage to be one wonderful thing and person. I love you girls. Tzuyu.. I understand you are tense for your solo debut (it's natural I think) but be yourself and you will be great as you always are. You always try so hard, you are the youngest member of Twice but you are always great in every situation. It's true, sometimes you don't speak much and in interviews you have to talk to explain feelings of making a solo debut, of the process of the recording, about the songs and so on but be yourself and say what you feel like saying and that comes from inside you in a natural way. You will be great💖. Remember we love you for who you are and sometimes not being too talkative makes you even more charming😀😁. You will be great I'm sure of it and Onces will be there to support you (remember there is always the chat with your sisters too💓). You are truly a great artist precious diamond... never forget it. I love you angels.💖💖💖
